---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'The Process',
  description: 'How The Matchmaking Bureau works — our five step matchmaking process. From application to introduction, every step is managed with precision and discretion.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <main transition:animate="fade">

    <section class="relative h-[614px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 overflow-hidden">
      <p class="tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-[#eac290] mb-6 text-xs" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">The Methodology of Excellence</p>
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-6xl tracking-tight text-white md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">The Process</h1>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#eac290]"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-32 px-6 py-24 md:space-y-48 md:px-24 md:py-32 lg:px-48">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <span class="block text-7xl leading-none text-[#eac290]/20 md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">01</span>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-[#4e453b] mt-8"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 pt-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[#eac290] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">The Application</h2>
          <p class="max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#d2c4b7] md:text-2xl" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Entry into The Matchmaking Bureau is by selective inquiry only. Your journey begins with a confidential digital application, where we assess fundamental alignment with our global community's standards of achievement and intent.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-4 text-[#eac290] uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Initial Screening & Vetting
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-8 order-2 md:order-1 pt-4 text-right flex flex-col items-end">
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[#eac290] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">The Consultation</h2>
          <p class="max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#d2c4b7] md:text-2xl" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            A deep-dive investigative interview conducted by our lead matchmakers. We look beyond statistics to understand your emotional intelligence, lifestyle nuances, and long-term vision, creating a bespoke blueprint for your search.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-4 text-[#eac290] uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Strategic Blueprinting
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-4 order-1 md:order-2">
          <span class="block text-right text-7xl leading-none text-[#eac290]/20 md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">02</span>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-[#4e453b] mt-8"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <span class="block text-7xl leading-none text-[#eac290]/20 md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">03</span>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-[#4e453b] mt-8"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 pt-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[#eac290] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">The Search</h2>
          <p class="max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#d2c4b7] md:text-2xl" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Our team reviews our private network and leverages a global circle of scouts. Every potential match is hand-vetted through rigorous background checks and face-to-face preliminary interviews before being presented.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-4 text-[#eac290] uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Private Network Review & Global Scouting
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-8 order-2 md:order-1 pt-4 text-right flex flex-col items-end">
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[#eac290] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">The Introduction</h2>
          <p class="max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#d2c4b7] md:text-2xl" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Introductions are orchestrated with precision. We manage the logistics of the first meeting, ensuring an environment conducive to authentic connection. Our role is to remove the friction of modern dating, leaving only the possibility.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-4 text-[#eac290] uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Managed First Encounters
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-4 order-1 md:order-2">
          <span class="block text-right text-7xl leading-none text-[#eac290]/20 md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">04</span>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-[#4e453b] mt-8"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <span class="block text-7xl leading-none text-[#eac290]/20 md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">05</span>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-[#4e453b] mt-8"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 pt-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[#eac290] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">Ongoing Support</h2>
          <p class="max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#d2c4b7] md:text-2xl" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Following every introduction, we facilitate a comprehensive feedback loop. This iterative process allows us to refine the search parameters continuously, providing ongoing coaching and concierge support throughout your courtship.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-4 text-[#eac290] uppercase tracking-widest text-xs" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            Feedback Loops & Concierge Coaching
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-24">
      <div class="bg-[#161b2b] border border-[#4e453b] p-12 md:p-24 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/3">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-[#eac290] mb-4" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">A Mandate of Absolute Discretion</h3>
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-[#eac290]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3">
          <p class="text-xl text-[#d2c4b7] italic leading-relaxed" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            "The Matchmaking Bureau operates in the shadows to preserve the reputations of our members. Our confidentiality protocols are modeled after private banking standards; no profiles are ever hosted publicly, and identities are only revealed when mutual interest and absolute safety are confirmed."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-48 text-center px-6 border-t border-[#4e453b]">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-4xl text-white md:text-7xl" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">Ready for a different kind of introduction?</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl text-xl text-[#d2c4b7] md:text-2xl" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
        We accept a limited number of new members each quarter to maintain the integrity of our bespoke service.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-[#cda777] text-[#573c15] px-12 py-6 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sm hover:bg-[#eac290] transition-colors duration-500" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
        Begin the Dialogue
      </a>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
